From 5c449ddbaba1c807c4674f92e5ebf6a887edb58c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Philipp Zabel <p.zabel@pengutronix.de>
Date: Fri, 27 Jun 2025 13:45:40 +0200
Subject: drm/panel: samsung-s6e8aa0: Drop MIPI_DSI_MODE_VSYNC_FLUSH flag
Git-commit: 5c449ddbaba1c807c4674f92e5ebf6a887edb58c
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
References: jsc#PED-13979 jsc#PED-14039 jsc#PED-14046 jsc#PED-14211 jsc#PED-14333 jsc#PED-14487 jsc#PED-14488 jsc#PED-14497 jsc#PED-14499 jsc#PED-15868

Drop the MIPI_DSI_MODE_VSYNC_FLUSH flag from DSI mode_flags.
It has no effect anymore.

Acked-by: Marek Szyprowski <m.szyprowski@samsung.com>
Acked-by: Neil Armstrong <neil.armstrong@linaro.org>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20250627-dsi-vsync-flush-v2-3-4066899a5608@pengutronix.de
Signed-off-by: Philipp Zabel <p.zabel@pengutronix.de>
Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>

---
 drivers/gpu/drm/panel/panel-samsung-s6e8aa0.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/panel/panel-samsung-s6e8aa0.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/panel/panel-samsung-s6e8aa0.c
index 897df195f2f3..1b5c500d4f4e 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/panel/panel-samsung-s6e8aa0.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/panel/panel-samsung-s6e8aa0.c
@@ -992,7 +992,7 @@ static int s6e8aa0_probe(struct mipi_dsi_device *dsi)
 	dsi->lanes = 4;
 	dsi->format = MIPI_DSI_FMT_RGB888;
 	dsi->mode_flags = MIPI_DSI_MODE_VIDEO | MIPI_DSI_MODE_VIDEO_BURST
-		| MIPI_DSI_MODE_VSYNC_FLUSH | MIPI_DSI_MODE_VIDEO_AUTO_VERT;
+		| MIPI_DSI_MODE_VIDEO_AUTO_VERT;
 
 	ret = s6e8aa0_parse_dt(ctx);
 	if (ret < 0)
